<p>This offline teaching system enables users to create NC (numerically controlled) programs and jigs for simultaneous 5-axis laser machining by the minimum amount of workload through the use of 3D CAD data.<br>It has been integrated with robust modelling functions of CADmeister. Thus, users can correct models and create laser machining data in one system.</p><p><br></p><h2 class="fr-text-bordered">Features</h2><h3>Intuitive Operability</h3><hr><p>3D LASER enables users to feel as if they are actually operating a laser machining device.</p><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/9EAC5F99-F882-1024-78FE-6865C1BCDD36.jpeg" width="450" height="266" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p align="center"><br></p><h3>Simulations and Interference Check</h3><hr><p>3D LASER enables users to simulate actual device movements through the use of machining data and thus to check interferences.</p><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/3337EC14-5F1C-8057-E574-3AB7487D9DB6.jpeg" width="450" height="266" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p align="center"><br></p><h3>Jig Design Functions</h3><hr><p>3D LASER enables users to design jigs based on the model data through the minimum amount of necessary inputs.</p><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/FC913108-98A5-D1B0-E67A-0B4DE569A70A.jpeg" width="450" height="268" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/496FC71F-77ED-8FDA-E276-AF97CC8FC19A.jpeg" width="520" height="207" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p align="center"><br></p><h3>Re-editing of NC Data</h3><hr><p>Any existing NC data can be imported and edited.</p><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/155DFFC2-570D-0D1F-DA8C-56ECA8ACD0E7.jpeg" width="520" height="215" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p align="center"><br></p><p align="center"><br></p><h3 class="fr-text-bordered">Inquiries</h3><p>If you have any inquiries about our product or would like to request a visit to your place for explanation or demonstration, please use the inquiry form.</p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/contact"><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Contact Us &rarr;</span></a></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p>